<http://www.isid.org>
Date: 20 Jan 2003
From: Dr. Daniel Elad <elad@agri.huji.ac.il>

The signs described for the lethargic turtles seem to be similar to those
reported for botulism in some other species. Has this possibility been
investigated?
--
Dr. Daniel Elad
Head, Dept. of Clinical Bacteriology and Mycology
(acting as National Botulism Reference Laboratory)
Kimron Veterinary Institute
Israel
<elad@agri.huji.ac.il>
[Dr. Elad presents an interesting question. If someone has done the testing
for botulism, please let us know. - Mod.TG]
